      • createJoin

        public JoinedQLBuilder createJoin(String associationPath)
        Description copied from interface: HQLBuilder
        Create an inner join with a shared alias.

        This is equivalent to calling createJoin(associationPath, CriteriaSpecification#INNER_JOIN)

        A new join is created for each unique combination of association path, join type, and alias, regardless of how many times createJoin is called with the same parameters.

        Specified by:
        createJoin in interface net.proteusframework.ui.search.HQLBuilder
        Parameters:
        associationPath - the association path.

        This is equivalent to calling createJoin(associationPath, joinType, createSharedAlias(associationPath)
